query_ac

Name
.SI 5
query_ac - Armour class calculation.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_ac(string type, int dam);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
The type is the type of attack, like "sharp" or "blunt".  The damage is
the amount of damage to do to the armour if it gets damaged.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
combat, attack
.EP
